OL,3,C'Out of control': Gambling adverts
OL,4,Ctriple in Premier League opening
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FEngland's most capped player, Peter
OL,8,FShilton, tells ITV News about his
OL,9,F'illness and addiction' to gambling
OL,10,Fand what needs to done
OL,12,FThe opening weekend of this season's
OL,13,FPremier League saw almost 30,000
OL,14,Fgambling adverts splashed across TV,
OL,15,Fradio and social media.
OL,17,FThat is three times more adverts than
OL,18,Fthe opening weekend last year.
