OL,3,C'Out of control': Gambling adverts
OL,4,Ctriple in Premier League opening
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FIn the West Ham United v Aston Villa
OL,8,Fmatch, there were 30 gambling adverts,
OL,9,Fmessages or logos on screen each
OL,10,Fminute.
OL,12,FUniversity of Bristol marketing
OL,13,Fresearcher Dr Raffaello Rossi, who
OL,14,Fconducted the study, said the gambling
OL,15,Findustry was "out of control".
OL,17,F"It's clear that the industry's
OL,18,Fattempt to self-regulate is wholly
OL,19,Finadequate and tokenistic," he said.
