OL,4,Ctriple in Premier League opening
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,F"The gambling industry continues to
OL,8,Fprioritise profit over safety."
OL,10,FFormer England goalkeeper Peter
OL,11,FShilton, who has experienced his own
OL,12,Fgambling problems, said gambling
OL,13,Fadvertisements were 'off the scale'
OL,14,Fand proved that gambling companies
OL,15,Fcould not regulate themselves.
OL,17,F"The great game of football is getting
OL,18,Fused to promote gambling and it's a
OL,19,Ffamily sport," he told ITV News.
