OL,7,F"More people are going to get involved
OL,8,Fin gambling, younger people as well.
OL,10,F"They advertise it as fun. It's not
OL,11,Ffun, it can take over your life."
OL,13,FThe research has renewed calls for the
OL,14,Fgovernment to urgently reform gambling
OL,15,Fadvertising, marketing and sponsorship.
