OL,7,F"With political will, these reforms
OL,8,Fcan be implemented now without the
OL,9,Fneed for new legislation," said Lord
OL,10,FFoster of Bath, who chairs Peers for
OL,11,FGambling Reform.
OL,13,F"These statistics reveal the woeful
OL,14,Finadequacies of industry self-
OL,15,Fregulation.
OL,17,F"It is simply not good enough."
