OL,7,FThe government said the gambling
OL,8,Fpolicy was under consideration at the
OL,9,Fmoment and it recognised the impact
OL,10,Fharmful gambling had.
OL,12,FBut a Betting and Gaming Council
OL,13,Fspokesman said the study had
OL,14,F"fundamentally misunderstood"
OL,15,Fadvertising and regulation.
OL,17,F"The previous government's stated
OL,18,Fresearch did not establish a causal
OL,19,Flink between exposure to advertising
OL,20,Fand the development of problem
OL,21,Fgambling."
