OL,7,F"Betting advertising and sponsorship
OL,8,Fmust comply with strict guidelines and
OL,9,Fsafer gambling tools and signposts to
OL,10,Fhelp for those concerned about their
OL,11,Fbetting, are regularly and prominently
OL,12,Fdisplayed."
OL,14,FAnyone experiencing harm directly from
OL,15,Fgambling or as an affected other can
OL,16,Fcall the National Gambling Helpline at
OL,17,F0808 8020 133, which is available 24/7
OL,18,Fand offers free, confidential advice,
OL,19,Ftools, and support.
